author: The Critical Drinker
description: He was once the king of big budget blockbusters, the chosen successor of Steven Spielberg, the man who rejuvinated not one but two of the biggest franchises in Hollywood - Star Trek AND Star Wars. Then it all came crashing down with one disastrous movie. Join me as I recount the rise and fall of JJ Abrams.
title: Crash And Burn - The JJ Abrams Story
